      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5625 - Yahya ibn Abi Imran narrated from Yunus from a man who narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) that he said: \"The grandfather and grandmother from the father's side and the grandfather and grandmother from the mother's side - all of them inherit.\""
        ]
